Sample code in Kotlin, interacting with TMDB API.
Using:
 Retrofit2,
 Dagger2,
 RxJava2,
 Picasso,
 Material Design,
 CardViews,
 RecyclerViews...

Testing with:
 JUnit testing,
 Robolectric,
 Mockito

